translation[5]{c,v,t}:
  28,1,Twâ-Sîn-Mîm
  28,2,Aga ni ma Ȃya ga m’Chitabu chakusalichisya
  28,3,"Tukunsoomela mmwe sine mwa abali sya Musa ni Firiauna mwakuonaonape, kwa ŵandu ŵaakukulupilila"
  28,4,"Chisimu Firiauna jwalikwesisye pa chilambo, ni ŵatesile achinsyene (chilambocho) kuŵa mikutula-mikutula, likuga line mwa jamanjao ŵalitondweye machili (ŵanache ŵa Israila ŵatesile kuŵa achikapolo), jwaliji nkusikita ŵanache ŵao ŵachilume ni kwalekaga umi ŵanache ŵao ŵachikongwe, chisimu jwalakwe jwaliji mwa akuwatanganya"
  28,5,"Ni twasachile kwatendela yaukoto aŵala ŵaŵatondoyedwe machili pa chilambo, ni kwatenda kuŵa achinnongola, ni kwatenda soni kuŵa ŵawinjila"